    "feat": {
        "name": "Brine May",
        "type": "stat_block_section",
        "subtype": "feat",
        "text": "Your mother was a sea hag, granting you one sea-green or blue eye. You find comfort both in the sea and on the shore. Whenever you roll a success on an Athletics check to Swim, you get a critical success instead. If you end your turn in water without having succeeded at a Swim action that round, you don\u2019t sink (but you might still be moved by the current).",
        "level": 1,
        "traits": [
